<div>
  <h1>Summary report of the presentation</h1>

  <% @reportComments.each do |comment| %>
    <div style='page-break-after:always;' style="padding-top: 1.5em;">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="panel panel-info">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h2>Comment Report Details</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="panel-body">
              <section class="col-md-6">
                  <h4>Group Number: <%= comment.group %></h4>
              </section>
              <section class="col-md-6">
                  <h4>Project Name: <%= comment.project %></h4>
              </section>

              <section class="col-md-12 form-group">
                <label class="comment_label">What are the strengths of this presentation(clarity, flow, delivery, visuals etc.)?</label><br/>
                <div class="comment_content">Comment: <%= comment.strength %></div>
              </section>

              <hr>

              <section class="col-md-12 form-group">
                <label class="comment_label">What are its primary weaknesses?</label><br/>
                <div class="comment_content">Comment: <%= comment.weakness %></div>
              </section>

              <hr>

              <section class="col-md-12 form-group">
                <label class="comment_label">Was it clear to you what improvement was being proposed and do you find its benefits compelling? Why or why not?</label><br/>
                <div class="comment_content">Comment: <%= comment.improvement %></div>
              </section>

              <hr>

              <section class="col-md-12 form-group">
                <label class="comment_label">If this were presented to you would you be inclined to agree to move ahead and fund this project?<small> (It is understood that you would probably require a lot of additional detailed information to make this decision. We are simply asking whether the high level idea and the approach, costs/benefits etc.) make this seem like a worthwhile project to you.</small></label><br/>
                <div class="comment_content">Comment: <%= comment.fund %></div>
              </section>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>


  <% @reportGrades.each do |grade| %>
    <div style='page-break-after:always;' style="padding-top: 1.5em;">
      
        <h1 class="grade-header">Grading Details</h1>

        <div class="grade-content">
            <div class="group-info clearfix">
              <p class="pull-left"><strong>Group #:</strong> <%= grade.group %></p>
              <p class="pull-right"><strong>Project Name:</strong> <%= grade.project %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="criteria">Does the presentation provide a complete and compelling explanation of: </div>

            <div class="question">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>a.</strong> The improvemnt opportnuity</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.opport %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content clearfix">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment:</span>
                   <div class="content">
                      <%= grade.opport_c %>
                   </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question clearfix">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>b.</strong> Costs and benefits</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.cost %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment:</span>
                   <div class="content">
                      <%= grade.cost_c %>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question clearfix">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>c.</strong> The approach and timeline</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.timeline %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content clearfix">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment:</span>
                   <div class="content">
                     <%= grade.timeline_c %>
                   </div> 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question clearfix">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>d.</strong> Key obstacles and how they will be addressed</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.obstacle %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content clearfix">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment:</span>
                   <div class="content">
                     <%= grade.obstacle %>
                   </div>   
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question clearfix">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>e.</strong> Risks and mitigation</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.risk %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content clearfix">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment:</span>
                   <div class="content">
                     <%= grade.risk_c %>
                   </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question clearfix">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>f.</strong> To what extent does the presentation address all the critical decision-points a senior executive would consider? If not, what do you feel is missing?</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.point %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content clearfix">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment: </span>
                   <div class="content">
                      <%= grade.point_c %>
                   </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question clearfix">
                <div class="col-md-6 question-section"><strong>g.</strong> Will the initiative will provide sufficient ROI and other benefits while minimizing risk, such that it is worth funding?</div>
                <h4 style="color: #b83936; padding-left: 10px;">Grade: <%= grade.fund %></h4>
                <div class="col-md-12 comment-content clearfix">
                   <span class="fa fa-comment"> Instructor Comment:</span>
                   <div class="content">
                      <%= grade.fund_c %>
                   </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="final-grade-section clearfix">
               <p class="pull-left">
                  <strong><span class="fa fa-calculator"></span> Final Grade:</strong>
                  <span class="final-grade"><%= grade.totalscore %></span>
               </p>
            </div>
          </div>


    </div>
  <% end %>


</div>
